Name: Van Maldergem syndrome 1
Definition: A Van Maldergem syndrome that has_material_basis_in homozygous mutation in the DCHS1 gene on chromosome 11p15.

Name: Van Maldergem syndrome 2
Definition: A Van Malergem syndrome that has_material_basis_in homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in the FAT4 gene on chromosome 4q28.
